comments: Antetokounmpo (MIL) extends his arm for the rebound and incidental contact occurs with Ball's (CHA) arm as he taps the ball to his teammate.
Ball (CHA) brings his off-arm toward Holiday's (MIL) front and marginal contact occurs as Ball releases away.
Hayward (CHA) establishes a wide screening position and initiates foot-to-foot contact with Holiday (MIL) as Holiday goes over, affecting his ability to defend.
Middleton (MIL) turns alongside Hayward's (CHA) path and marginal body contact occurs as Hayward drives toward the lane.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) is late to the spot and continues moving toward Washington (CHA) when he makes body contact that affects Washington's SQBR.
As Antetokounmpo (MIL) falls to the floor following the contact, his foot unintentionally makes contact with the ball.
Bridges (CHA) legally goes into the backcourt to retrieve the ball after Antetokounmpo (MIL) touches it.
Correctly called shot clock violation on CHA.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) brings his hands toward Bridges' (CHA) side as he sets the pick and marginal contact occurs as Antetokounmpo releases toward the perimeter.
Middleton (MIL) and Washington (CHA) make incidental foot-to-foot contact with one another as they return to the floor following the pass.
Hayward (CHA) brings his right hand toward Holiday's (MIL) front and marginal contact occurs before Holiday slips and falls to the floor during rebounding.
Washington (CHA) brings his hands toward Allen's (MIL) side and marginal contact occurs as Washington releases away to roll.
Holiday (MIL) legally contests Rozier's (CHA) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Hayward (CHA) and Connaughton (MIL) each make clean contact with the ball before any incidental arm contact occurs during rebounding.
Washington (CHA) brushes Antetokounmpo's (MIL) left arm and marginal contact occurs at the end of the drive.
Bridges (CHA) firms up in his screening position in Holiday's (MIL) path and absorbs the contact.
Connaughton (MIL) maintains a rested hand on Ball's (CHA) side and marginal contact occurs as Ball drives into the lane.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Ball (CHA) touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds.
